headline: 3 Reasons LOW is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Lowe’s shares (currently trading at $236.21) have posted a disappointing 8.1% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 3.6% gain. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
